      "content": "Hey, I need help polishing this abstract for a submission to Nature. The topic is \"AI Cognitive Limits in Large Language Models.\" I really need this to sound high-impact and rigorous because the reviewers at Nature are incredibly picky about methodology and scale. Here is the rough draft:\n\n\"This study investigates the cognitive boundaries of LLMs through a series of behavioral testing protocols. We observed significant deviations in reasoning consistency when subjected to high-entropy prompts, suggesting inherent structural limitations in current transformer architectures.\"\n\nCan you rewrite this to be more compelling and sophisticated for a top-tier journal? I want it to sound like a definitive, heavyweight study.",
